---
title: Meet Our Team
layout: default
---

<div class="mt-16 relative px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
  <div class="prose prose-lg lg:text-xl text-gray-500 mx-auto">
    <p>
      Our goal is always to provide the best service we can at justifiable
      rates. Our professional staff are committed to using the full
      capabilities of technology to provide you the best service we can.
      Working with us also always includes contact with partners as we seek
      to give you the best outcomes possible.
    </p>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="bg-white">
  <div class="mx-auto pt-12 px-4 max-w-7xl sm:px-6 lg:px-8 lg:pt-24">
    <div class="space-y-12">
      <ul role="list" class="space-y-12 sm:grid sm:grid-cols-2 sm:gap-x-6 sm:gap-y-12 sm:space-y-0 lg:grid-cols-3 lg:gap-x-8">
        {%- set persons = collections.people | first %}
        {%- for person in persons.data.members -%}
          <li x-data="{open: false}">
            <div class="space-y-4">
              <div class="aspect-w-3 aspect-h-2 overflow-y-hidden">
                {% image person.image, person.name, "w-full h-full object-cover shadow-lg rounded-lg" %}
              </div>

              <div class="space-y-2">
                <div class="text-lg leading-6 font-medium space-y-1">
                  <h3>{{person.name}}</h3>
                  <p class="text-blue-700">{{person.job_title}}</p>
                </div>

                <ul role="list" class="flex space-x-8">
                  {% if person.email_address %}
                    <li>
                      <a target="_blank" href="mailto:{{person.email_address}}" class="flex text-gray-400 hover:text-gray-500">
                        <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M2.003 5.884L10 9.882l7.997-3.998A2 2 0 0016 4H4a2 2 0 00-1.997 1.884z"></path><path d="M18 8.118l-8 4-8-4V14a2 2 0 002 2h12a2 2 0 002-2V8.118z"></path></svg>
                        <span class="ml-2">Email</span>
                      </a>
                    </li>
                  {% endif %}
                  <li>
                    <button
                      type="button"
                      class="bg-white flex text-base text-gray-400 hover:text-gray-500 focus:outline-none focus:ring-none"
                      @click="open = true"
                    >
                      <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 9a3 3 0 100-6 3 3 0 000 6zm-7 9a7 7 0 1114 0H3z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path></svg>
                      <span class="ml-1">Bio</span>
                    </button>

                  </li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
            <template x-teleport="body">
              <div
                x-show="open"
                @keydown.escape="open=false"
                role="dialog"
                aria-modal="true"
                x-id="['{{person.name}}-modal']"
                :aria-labelledby="$id('{{person.name}}-modal')"
                class="fixed inset-0 z-10"
              >
                <!-- overlay -->
                <div
                  class="fixed inset-0 bg-gray-500 bg-opacity-75
                         transition-opacity"
                  aria-hidden="true"
                  @click="open = false"
                ></div>

                <div
                  @click="open = false"
                  x-show="open"
                  x-transition
                  class="relative h-full w-full flex items-center
                           justify-center">
                  <div
                    @click.stop
                    class="max-w-2xl w-full rounded-lg bg-white p-12
                            overflow-y-auto shadow-xl transform transition-all"
                  >
                    <div class="block absolute top-0 right-0 pt-8 pr-8">
                      <button type="button" class="bg-white rounded-md
                                    text-gray-400 text:gray-500
                                    focus:outline-none focus:ring-2
                                    focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-gray-500"
                        @click="open = false"
                      >
                        <span class="sr-only">Close</span>
                        <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4.293 4.293a1 1 0 011.414 0L10 8.586l4.293-4.293a1 1 0 111.414 1.414L11.414 10l4.293 4.293a1 1 0 01-1.414 1.414L10 11.414l-4.293 4.293a1 1 0 01-1.414-1.414L8.586 10 4.293 5.707a1 1 0 010-1.414z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path></svg>
                      </button>
                    </div>
                    <div class="mt-12 prose">
                      {% image person.image, person.name, "w-full h-full object-cover shadow-lg rounded-lg" %}
                      <h2 class="text-3xl font-medium"
                          :id="$id('{{person.name}}-modal')">
                        {{person.name}}
                      </h2>

                      {{person.body | markdown | safe}}
                    </div>
                    <div class="mt-10 text-center">
                      <button
                        type="button"
                        class="bg-white text-sm text-gray-500 hover:text-gray-700
                               focus:outline-none focus:ring-none"
                        @click="open = false"
                      >
                        Close
                      </button>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </template>
          </li>

        {% endfor %}
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="relative my-16 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
  <div class="prose prose-lg lg:text-xl text-gray-500 mx-auto">
    <p>
      We work tirelessly to ensure the best outcomes for our clients. Ready to
      see what the accountants and staff at <b>Buckley &amp; Sitzman, LLP</b>
      can do for you and your business?
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="max-w-prose text-center mx-auto">
    <p class="mt-10">
      <a
        href="/contact-us"
        class="inline-flex text-black items-center uppercase py-3 px-4 rounded-md
               hover:bg-secondary-600 bg-secondary-500 font-medium
               focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-offset-2
               focus:ring-secondary-400 focus:ring-offset-gray-900"
      >
        Contact Us
      </a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
